{"type": "article", "id": 40662, "title": "为猫设计的家具，也可以当成家居装饰品｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-10T23:21:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 413, "name": "耳机"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 1108, "name": "相机"}, {"id": 1510, "name": "猫"}, {"id": 2446, "name": "边桌"}, {"id": 4337, "name": "酒瓶"}, {"id": 6294, "name": "吊灯"}, {"id": 152, "name": "徕卡"}, {"id": 15888, "name": "本土创造"}, {"id": 28065, "name": "Master & Dynamic"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 120, "image": "img/article/article_show/201705102031530IJFhi1AtwQjCHzN.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「<b>BestDesign</b>」或是「<b>Qthings</b>」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Decanter bottle for Canadian winery Stratus Vineyards by Karim Rashid</h3><p>以艺术风格闻名世界的纽约设计师 Karim Rashid 是酒瓶包装设计领域的专家，最近他为加拿大安大略省云彩酒庄（Stratus Vineyards）设计了一款酒瓶，想要一改传统葡萄酒瓶的保守形象，创造出突破性的轮廓，“我们为什么不把传统的酒瓶砍掉呢？”他尝试将一个酒瓶切分成四块，并将这四个部分堆叠在一起，每个部分稍稍偏移出中心位置，使其在倾倒时更容易握住。最近，这款酒瓶正在办公家具品牌 Teknion 的纽约展厅展出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203221Mk8gKGJBstWL9qy5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.585871\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203222nNqwcSJoVZRBba7f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334602\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203258hVupmsxjiGJn5CBE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/05/09/decanter-karim-rashid-wine-bottle-stratus-vineyards/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Flat-pack Lumber table studio PESI</h3><p>首尔设计工作室 PESI 使用木纸板设计了一款边桌，希望借此来探讨纸板作为短期使用家具材料的可能性。它改变了一半纸板家具采用的折叠、层压的方式，改用 PVC 铆钉固定的形式，提供 11 种不同的木纸板材料，以及蓝色、红色、黄色、绿色和天然纸板棕色 5 种配色，允许买家自由组合。这款采用平板包装的边桌还收获了今年 ein&amp;zwanzig 设计大赛的奖项。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203415fCv4rwP1Xz7oJ0Uj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203418n6aNmJYRGbvSoZ2t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675973\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203418IOAvi3k71KqTSU2J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203419zw567BdDlovTxeki.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203418M3FHkSQ1zdRrxGv7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/05/09/pesi-lumber-table-cardboard-furniture-milan-design-week/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>YARFIE by Aelfie &amp; Michael Yarinsky</h3><p>Aelfie 和她的先生 Michael Yarinsky、女儿以及猫咪共同居住在纽约布鲁克林。他们想要为猫做一款家具，同时也希望即便家中没有猫，这款家具也能够成为如同雕塑艺术品一般的存在。Michael Yarinsky 本就是一位跨学科设计师，Ettore Sottsass、Namuchi Isamu 和 Peter Shire 等艺术家的作品给予了他灵感，他尝试使用数控磨灰胶合板与平纹编织材料制作家具，也可以说是猫咪的大型玩具。这一系列作品正在 Michael Yarinsky 主理的 Cooler Gallery 展出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203502v3Luiz2tOFTDfSMG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203502Fvne5M0RZTlNxUQj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203503msiu3Hctr1N6bYfB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.053906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203502M5zyRZYJEUW6mI93.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.012500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203503gtyATpYqX7amuWRw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.767969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203504kzitYNBagQ3l4ycE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675781\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Designmilk</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Terrazzo Series by Bentudesign</h3><p>陶瓷是一种历经了几千年中华文明煅烧的材质，这是国内原创家居品牌本土创造设计的，以材质再生为基本手段的水磨石系列，将陶瓷废渣再生成简洁形态的日常性家具。尤其是这款吊灯“棒”，陶瓷废渣被搅拌成细碎的黑白颗粒，均匀散布在灯身表面，呈现出与传统陶瓷气质相迥异的当代感，水磨石的肌理与金色的铜质配件混合搭配，还收获了 2017 年 iF 设计大奖的产品类别奖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203550c1uGosMk2YveplKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.024917\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705102035521kx6uP7q4QGFSoHT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.006601\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203552qZuDexQ8Xp0I56ft.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203555Ygm90DR5wjUtbA3I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.086379\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203555d4vp3ZCLuVJ7oHa2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662810\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203555OEf2er1khogdQ37S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665563\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：本土创造</figcaption></figure></div><h3>CROZ by Paper Shoot &amp; Hyle</h3><p>来自台湾的摄影器材公司 Paper Shoot 联手澳门设计师 Hyle 合作设计了一款透明数码相机 CROZ。透明的外壳选用了独特的亚克力材质制作而成，它的好处在于使用者可以根据自己的喜好 DIY 外壳。因为结构简单的缘故，CROZ 的机身重量仅有 48 克。值得一提的是，CROZ 有一个滤镜效果切换键，可以选择冷光、暖光、彩色以及黑白 4 种不同的滤镜进行拍摄。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=m05010uqi7w&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203657NCx5zMd7w2GvqZuk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769531\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203657nTx9dgD047t1aPeF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203657018cHo2S4QKUAJhG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203658nopCTRtBzI0bZUMD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.726563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510203657RxTc6doi2yuDL0qt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/technology/paper-shoot-hyle-design-croz-diy-camera-08-05-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Master &amp; Dynamic for 0.95 Leica Signature Collection</h3><p>美国高端耳机厂商 Master &amp; Dynamic 最近与徕卡相机公司合作，以“Master &amp; Dynamic for 0.95”为名，设计了三款耳机。这三款耳机的原型分别为 Master &amp; Dynamic 的 MW60 头戴式无线耳机、MH40 头戴式有线耳机和 ME05 纯铜版耳机。这次的合作款印有“0.95”的标志，采用柔韧的牛皮和不锈钢组件，细节处更是有与徕卡相机的转盘相仿的刻纹，和徕卡传奇镜头的标志性玻璃红点元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=v05014afh3m&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510204143eOfpjHwvRQYIKyXC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510204143Ue6va7yNDTFOikBM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510204143dAkBL20oHsRiXM8n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510204144fyK8nhLGd5T6mAPJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668704\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/technology/leica-camera-master-dynamic-headphones-04-28-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><p><br></p>"}